• ☂ Tassel design umbrella will add a fresh look and unique appearance to your beach or outdoor moment. Ideal for the beach, patio, backyard, lawn, pool, and garden
• ☂ The canopy can provide UPF50+ protection and block over 98% UV rays, keep you cool and comfortable, tilt feature with push-button to provide optimal shade as the sun moves
• ☂ 1.1/1.26'' steel pole and 8 fiberglass ribs provide elegance and superior strength support-Allow the umbrella stability in windy conditions

• ☂ Notes: Owing to differences in display settings and varying indoor/outdoor lighting conditions, minor color discrepancies may be noticeable on the umbrella
